### API Test İstekleri
### VS Code REST Client eklentisi ile kullanabilirsiniz

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5039

### 1. İlk Ürünü Ekle
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "description": "Gaming Laptop - 16GB RAM, RTX 3060",
  "price": 25000,
  "stock": 10,
  "category": "Elektronik",
  "sku": "LPT-001",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/laptop.jpg",
  "sellerId": "seller123",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 2. İkinci Ürünü Ekle
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Klavye",
  "description": "Mekanik RGB Klavye",
  "price": 1500,
  "stock": 50,
  "category": "Bilgisayar Aksesuarları",
  "sku": "KLV-001",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/keyboard.jpg",
  "sellerId": "seller123",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 3. Tüm Ürünleri Listele
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

###

### 4. Satıcıya Göre Ürünleri Listele
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?sellerId=seller123

###

### 5. Excel Şablonu İndir
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/template

###

### 6. Ürünleri Excel'e Aktar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/export?sellerId=seller123

###

### 7. Sipariş Ekle
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sellerId": "seller123",
  "customerId": "customer001",
  "customerName": "Ahmet Yılmaz",
  "customerEmail": "ahmet@example.com",
  "customerPhone": "05551234567",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "prod123",
      "productName": "Laptop",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 25000,
      "totalPrice": 25000
    }
  ],
  "totalAmount": 25000,
  "status": "Pending",
  "shippingAddress": "İstanbul, Türkiye"
}

###

### 8. Kargo Takip Ekle
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shipping
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "order123",
  "trackingNumber": "TK123456789",
  "carrier": "Aras Kargo",
  "status": "Shipped",
  "currentLocation": "İstanbul"
}

###

### 9. Kargo Şablonu İndir
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shipping/template

###
